# Modern UI Stack

- Build UI using Tailwind CSS utility classes as the default styling approach.
- Prefer `shadcn/ui` components for accessible, reusable primitives.
- Use Magic UI components for premium sections, motion-rich blocks, and hero visuals.
- Avoid ad-hoc CSS unless a utility-first or component-based approach cannot solve the need.
- Keep spacing, typography, and color usage consistent with a defined design token mindset.
